channel.title: My Models [ Explaining Topic ]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I know that some of you would like to see my models, and the progress that I am making on them. But I have been informed by Frell that my models are too High of a Resolution to be posted in the RS Models section, so if you would like to view my models, please take a look at the Graphics section. I will be posting all my Non-RS Client (Higher then 2k Poly) models there from now on.
Hoping that you will have a blast when overviewing my models ;) And maybe learn something from them, like a clean topology.
Yours truly,
A.C.F. :)
